text: Go, Dog. Go! is an American animated educational preschool television series developed by Adam Peltzman. It aired on Netflix on January 26, 2021. The show stars Michela Luci, Callum Shoniker, Katie Griffin, Martin Roach, Tajja Isen, Lyon Smith, Judy Marshank, Patrick McKenna and Linda Ballantyne. The characters in the show are Tag Barker, Scooch Pooch, Ma Barker, Paw Barker, Cheddar Biscuit, Spike Barker, Gilber Barker, Grandma Marge Barker, Grandpaw Mort Barker, Yip Barker, Sgt Pooch, and other characters. == References == == Other websites == * * * * * Category:Fictional dogs Category:Canadian children's television series Category:American children's television series Category:2020s American animated television series Category:Canadian animated television series Category:English-language television programs
